Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present for sale this A-grade commercial office investment located within the heart of Subiaco.

22 Railway Road, Subiaco is an ultra-modern commercial office building completed late 2006. Office suite 12 is positioned front and centre on Level 1, taking advantage of favourable aspects and of superior presentation.

- Fully leased to established high calibre tenant.
-  Superbly fitout 167sqm offices plus balcony and 4 secured car bays at basement
-  Strong net income $108,650pa with built in growth 4%pa, market review at option
-  Secured by new 3 years lease renewal until 1st January 2017 plus 3 years option
-  Priced at $1,448,500 (No GST - Going Concern) for prompt sale.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FOR SALE - LEASED OFFICE INVESTMENT, SUBIACO, WA - 7.5%PA NET (APPROX)

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A new opportunity has become available on popular Rokeby Road, Subiaco.

The 116sqm tenancy is located next to other retailers including:
-  San Churro
-  Mecca Cosmetica
-  GazMan
-  Bang & Olufsen
- Jus Burger
- Wagamama's

The opportunity is suitable for a variety of uses including Food and Beverage.

Located in the Subiaco town centre, this tenancy represents a rare opportunity for retailers to secure a first class site in this tightly held area.

The site is adjacent to the soon to be redeveloped Subiaco Markets and in close proximity to Rokeby Road and a Wilson car park.
The tenancy is located in the 'Town Centre' zone of Subiaco which allows flexibility in relation to retail uses.

Available immediately, the site is located on the southern side of Roberts Road in the Subiaco Town Centre, only metres away from from the main retailing strips of Rokeby Road & Hay Street.

Subiaco is located only 3 kilomentres from the Perth CBD and 5 kilometres south of the Bulky Goods capital of Perth, Osborne Park.
The site has over 18,820 cars passing per day.

Currently under construction, this showroom represents a rare opportunity to enter the tightly held retail/showroom strip on Hay Street, Subiaco. A variety of strong showroom/retail tenants including Bose Sound, Monro Furniture, Designed Kitchen appliances, Living with Innovation and Officeworks are located in close proximity to this site.

The building will be constructed to a superior standard including large glass shop front windows to maximize display exposure to Hay Street.

The site is due forcompletion date Late 2009

CBRE is pleased to offer for sale 198 Nicholson Road, Subiaco.

The property comprises 115sqm* of building area situated on a rectangular shaped allotment of 521sqm*, ideally located within walking distance to Nicholson Road’s thriving retail and commercial strip.

Zoned ‘Neighbourhood Mixed Use’ under the City of Subiaco’s Town Planning Scheme No. 4, permitted uses include medical centre, local shop or single dwelling.

The property is offered with vacant possession via offers to purchase invited, closing Wednesday 9th October 2019 at 4pm.

For further details, or to request the information memorandum, please contact the exclusive selling agents CBRE.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PRIME SUBIACO LOCATION – OCCUPY, INVEST OR REDEVLEOP
